{"title":"朱德的扁担","authors":["肖韶光"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱德的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山的翠竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着挺直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒下依然挺直"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然生存状态改变了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟亮节不变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根竹制的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他的手里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗起为柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支撑华夏阴晴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横着当梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担挑江山冷暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰难岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了一座摇篮的命运"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须挑粮上山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时官兵平等"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平等成一副担的两个筐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军长挑粮的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常被士兵争先抢走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使他不得不给“自家的农具”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做个记号——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“朱德扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准乱拿”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那段食盐奇缺的岁月他用带咸的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溶开一道道封锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给大地充满生机的湿润"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历经沧桑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱德的扁担枣红锃亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不需要任何装饰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及防腐剂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"释放出一种无法抗拒的穿透力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起朱德的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前就现出军长肩挑的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国极为普遍又普通"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惟有他的这种姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在几代人心目中定型成不朽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时常想起朱德的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会使人猛然觉得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩头上的分量重了许多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脊梁便会更加挺拔起来"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}